quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  5,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  5,1,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, bandishon ki poori pabandi karo tumahray liye mawayshi ki qisam ke sab janwar halal kiye gay, siwaye unn ke jo agay chal kar tum ko betaye jayen ge lekin ahraam ki haalat mein shikaar ko apne liye halal nah kar lau, be shak Allah jo chahta hai hukum deta hai"
  5,2,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, khuda parasti ki nshanyon ko be hurmat nah karo nah haraam mahino mein se kisi ko halal kar lau, nah qurbani ke janwaron par dast Darazi karo, nah unn janwaron par haath daalo jin ki gardnon mein Nazar khuda wandi ki alamat ke tor par pitay parre hue hon, nah unn logon ko chairo jo apne rab ke fazl aur is ki khushnodi ki talaash mein makaan mohtaram ( kaaba ) ki taraf ja rahay hon haan jab ahraam ki haalat khatam ho jaye to shikaar tum kar saktay ho aur dekho, aik giroh ne jo tumahray liye masjid haraam ka rasta band kar diya hai twas par tumhara gussa tumhe itna mushtael nah kar day ke tum bhi un ke muqaabla mein naarwa zyadtyan karne lagu nahi! jo kaam neki aur khuda tarsi ke hain un mein sab se taawun karo aur jo gunah aur zayad-ti ke kaam hain un mein kisi se taawun nah karo Allah se daro, is ki sz a bohat sakht hai"
  5,3,"tum par haraam kya gaya Murdaar, khoon, soor ka gosht, woh janwar jo khuda ke siwa kisi aur ke naam par zibah kya gaya ho, woh jo ghulla ghatt kar, ya chout kha kar, ya bulandi se gir kar, ya takkar kha kar mra ho, ya jisay kisi darendey ne pharha ho siwaye is ke jisay tum ne zindah paker zibah kar liya aur woh jo kisi Aasta ne par zibah kya gaya ho neez yeh bhi tumahray liye najaaiz hai ke panson ke zareya se apni qismat maloom karo yeh sab af-aal fisq hain aaj kafiroon ko tumahray deen ki taraf se poori mayoosi ho chuki hai lehaza tum unn se nah daro balkay mujh se daro aaj mein ne tumahray deen ko tumahray liye mukammal kar diya hai aur apni Nemat tum par tamam kar di hai aur tumahray liye islam ko tumahray deen ki hesiyat se qubool kar liya hai ( lehaza haraam o halal ki jo quyood tum par aed kar di gayi hain unn ki paband y karo ) Albata jo shakhs bhook se majaboor ho kar unn mein se koi cheez kha le, baghair is ke ke gunah ki taraf is ka melaan ho to bay shak Allah maaf karne wala aur reham frmane wala hai"
  5,4,"log puchhte hain ke un ke liye kya halal kya gaya hai, kaho tumahray liye saari pak cheeze halal kar di gayi hain aur jin shikari janwaron ko tum ne sadhaeya ho jin ko khuda ke diye hue ilm ki bana par tum shikaar ki taleem diya karte ho woh jis janwar ko tumahray liye pakar rakhen is ko bhi tum kha saktayho, Albata is par Allah ka naam le lau aur Allah ka qanoon tornay se daro, Allah ko hisaab letay kuch der nahi lagti"
  5,5,"aaj tumahray liye saari pak cheeze halal kar di gayi hain ahal kitaab ka khana tumahray liye halal hai aur tumhara khana unn ke liye aur mehfooz aurtain bhi tumahray liye halal hain khuwa woh ahal imaan ke giroh se hon ya unn qomon mein se jin ko tum se pehlay kitaab di gayi thi, bashar tik_h tum unn ke mohar ada kar ke nikah mein unn ke Muhafiz bano, nah yeh ke azad shehwat rani karne lagu ya chori chupay آ(ashnaiya-nkaro aur jo kisi ne imaan ki rawish par chalne se inkaar kya to is ka sara karnaama zindagi zaya ho jaye ga aur woh akhirat mein dewalia hoga"
  5,6,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, jab tum namaz ke liye utho to chahiye ke apne mun aur haath kohniyo-n taq dho lu, siro-n par haath phair lu aur paontalkhno-n taq dho liya karo agar janabat ki haalat mein ho to neha kar pak ho jao agar bemaar ho ya safar ki haalat mein ho ya tum mein se koi shakhs rafa haajat kar ke aeye ya tum ne aurton ko haath lagaya ho, aur pani nah miley, to pak matti se kaam lau, bas uss par haath maar kar apne mun aur hathon par phair liya karo Allah tum par zindagi ko tang nahi karna chahta, magar woh chahta hai ke tumhe pak kere aur apni Nemat tum par tamam kar day, shayad ke tum shukar guzaar bano"
  5,7,"Allah ne tum ko jo Nemat ataa ki hai is ka khayaal rakho aur uss pukhta ehad o Paiman ko nah bhulo jo uss ne tum se liya hai, yani tumhara yeh qoul ke,"" hum ne suna aur itaat qubool ki"" Allah se daro, Allah dilon ke raaz taq jaanta hai"
  5,8,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho! Allah ki khatir raasti par qaim rehne walay aur insaaf ki gawahi dainay walay bano kisi giroh ki dushmani tum ko itna mushtael nah kar day ke insaaf se phir jao Adal karo, yeh khuda tarsi se ziyada munasbat rakhta hai Allah se dar kar kaam karte raho, jo kuch tum karte ho Allah uss se poori terhan bakhabar hai"
  5,9,"jo log imaan layein aur naik amal karen, Allah ne un se wada kya hai ke un ki khataon se dar guzar kya jaye ga aur inhen bara ajar miley ga"
  5,10,rahay woh log jo kufar karen aur Allah ki ayaat ko jhutla-ay-n to woh dozakh mein jaane walay hain
  5,11,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, Allah ke uss ahsaan ko yaad karo jo uss ne ( abhi haal mein ) tum par kya hai, jabkay aik giroh ne tum par dast Darazi ka iradah kar liya tha magar Allah ne unn ke haath tum par uthnay se rok diye Allah se dar kar kaam karte raho, imaan rakhnay walon ko Allah hi par bharosa karna chahiye"
  5,12,"Allah ne bani Israel se pukhta ehad liya tha aur un mein baara naqeeb muqarrar kiye thay aur un se kaha tha ke"" mein tumahray sath hon, agar tum ne namaz qaim rakhi aur zkoh di aur mere Rasolo-n ko maana aur un ki madad ki aur apne khuda ko acha qarz dete rahay to yaqeen rakho ke mein tumhari buraiyan tum se zael kar dun ga aur tum ko aisay baghoon mein daakhil karoon ga jin ke neechay nhrin behti hon gi, mgras ke baad jis ne tum mein se kufar ki rawish ikhtiyar ki to Dur haqeeqat uss neswa as sabeelgum kar di """
  5,13,"phir yeh unn ka apne ehad ko toar daalna tha jis ki wajah se hum ne un ko apni rehmat se daur pheink diya aur un ke dil sakht kar diye ab un ka haal yeh hai ke alfaaz ka ulat phair kar ke baat ko kahin se kahin le jatay hain, jo taleem inhen di gayi thi uss ka bara hissa bhool chuke hain, aur aeye din tumhe un ki kisi nah kisi khayanat ka pata chalta rehta hai un mein se bohat kam log is aib se bachay hue hain ( pas jab yeh iss haal ko poanch chuke hain to jo sharartein bhi yeh karen woh un se ain mutawaqqa hain ) lehaza inhen maaf karo aur un ki harkaat se chasham poshi karte raho, Allah unn logon ko pasand karta hai jo ahsaan ki rawish rakhtay hain"
  5,14,"isi terhan hum ne unn logon se bhi pukhta ehad liya tha jinhon ne kaha tha ke hum"" nasari"" hain, magar un ko bhi jo sabaq yaad karaya gaya tha is ka aik bara hissa onhon ne faramosh kar diya aakhir-kaar hum ne un ke darmain qayamat taq ke liye dushmani aur aapas ke bughz o inaad ka beej bo diya, aur zaroor aik waqt aeye ga jab Allah inhen betaye ga ke woh duniya mein kya banatay rahay hain"
  5,15,"ae ahal kitaab! hamara rasool tumahray paas aa gaya hai jo kitaab Ellahi ki bohat si unn baton ko tumahray samnay khol raha hai jin par tum parda dala karte thay, aur bohat si baton se dar guzar bhi kar jata hai tumahray paas Allah ki taraf se roshni aa gayi hai aur aik aisi haq numa kitaab"
  5,16,jis ke zareya se Allah taala unn logon ko jo is ki Raza ke taalib hain salamti ke tareeqay batata hai aur apne azan se unn ko andheron se nikaal kar ujalay ki taraf lata hai aur raah raast ki taraf un ki rahnumai karta hai
  5,17,"yaqeenan kufar kya unn logon ne jinhon ne kaha maseeh Ibn maryam hi khuda hai ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! un se kaho ke agar khuda maseeh Ibn maryam ko aur is ki maa aur tamam zameen walon ko halaak kar dena chahay to kis ki majaal hai ke uss ko iss iraday se baz rakh sakay? Allah to zameen aur asmano ka aur unn sab cheezon ka maalik hai jo zameen aur asmano ke darmain payi jati hain, jo kuch chahta hai peda karta hai aur is ki qudrat har cheez par haawi hai"
  5,18,"yahood aur nasari kehte hain ke hum Allah ke betay aur is ke chaheetey hain un se pucho, phir woh tumahray gunaaho par tumhe saza kyun deta hai? Dur haqeeqat tum bhi waisay hi ensaan ho jaisay aur ensaan khuda ne peda kiye hain woh jisay chahta hai maaf karta hai aur jisay chahta hai saza deta hai zameen aur aasman aur un ki saari mojoodaat is ki Malik hain, aur isi ki taraf sab ko jana hai"
  5,19,"ae ahal kitaab! hamara yeh rasool aisay waqt tumahray paas aaya hai aur deen ki wazeh taleem tumhe day raha hai jabkay Rasolo-n ki aamad ka silsila aik muddat se band tha, taakay tum yeh nah keh sakuu ke hamaray paas koi basharat dainay wala aur darane wala nahi aaya so dekho! ab woh basharat dainay aur darane wala aa gaya aur Allah har cheez par Qadir hai"
  5,20,"yaad karo jab moose ne apni qoum se kaha tha ke"" ae meri qoum ke logo! Allah ki uss Nemat ka khayaal karo jo is ne tumhe ataa ki thi uss ne tum mein nabi peda kiye, tum ko farmaa rawa banaya, aur tum ko woh kuch diya jo duniya mein kisi ko nah diya tha"
  5,21,"ae baradran qoum! is muqaddas sarzamen mein daakhil ho jao jo Allah ne tumahray liye likh di hai, peechay nah hato warna nakaam o namuraad paltoo ge """
  5,22,"unhon ne jawab diya"" ae moose! wahan to barray zabardast log rehtay hain, hum wahan hargiz nah jayen ge jab taq woh wahan se nikal nah jayen haan agar woh nikal gay to hum daakhil honay ke liye tayyar hain """
  5,23,"unn darny walon mein do shakhs aisay bhi thay jin ko Allah ne apni Nemat se nawaza tha onhon ne kaha ke"" un jabbaroon ke muqaabla mein darwazay ke andar ghis jao, jab tum andar poanch jao ge to tum hi ghalib raho ge Allah par bharosa rakho agar tum momin ho """
  5,24,"lekin onhon ne phir yahi kaha ke"" ae moose! hum to wahan kabhi nah jayen ge jab taq woh wahan mojood hain bas tum aur tumhara rab, dono jao aur lrho, hum yahan baithy hain """
  5,25,"is par moose ne kaha"" ae mere rab, mere ikhtiyar mein koi nahi magar ya meri apni zaat ya mera bhai, pas to hamein inn nafarman logon se allag kar day """
  5,26,"Allah ne jawab diya"" acha to woh malik chalees saal taq inn par haraam hai, yeh zameen mein maaray maaray phrin ge, inn na farmanoon ki haalat par hargiz taras nah khao """
  5,27,"aur zara inhen aadam ke do beton ka qissa bhi be kam o kaast suna do jab unn dono ne qurbani ki to un mein se aik ki qurbani qubool ki gayi aur dosray ki nah ki gayi uss ne kaha"" mein tujhe maar daloon ga"" is ne jawab diya"" Allah tomuttaqi yoo-n hi ki nazren qubool karta hai"
  5,28,"agar to mujhe qatal karne ke liye haath uthaye ga to mein tujhe qatal karne ke liye haath nah uthaoun ga, mein Allah rab alameen se darta hon"
  5,29,"mein chahta hon ke mera aur apna gunah to hi samaitt le aur dozakhi ban kar rahay zaalmon ke zulm ka yahi theek badla hai """
  5,30,aakhir-kaar is ke nafs ne apne bhai ka qatal is ke liye aasaan kar diya aur woh usay maar kar unn logon mein shaamil ho gaya jo nuqsaan uthany walay hain
  5,31,phir Allah ne aik kuaa bheja jo zameen khodnay laga taakay ussay betaye ke apne bhai ki laash kaisay chupaye yeh dekh kar woh bola afsos mujh par! mein is kaway jaissa bhi nah ho saka ke apne bhai ki laash chupaney ki tadbeer nikaal laita is ke baad woh apne kiye par bohat pchhta ya
  5,32,"isi wajah se bani Israel par hum ne yeh farmaan likh diya tha ke"" jis ne kisi ensaan ko khoon ke badlay ya zameen mein fasaad phelanay ke siwa kisi aur wajah se qatal kya is ne goya tamam insanon ko qatal kar diya aur jis ne kisi ki jaan bachaai uss ne goya tamam insanon ko zindagi bakhash di"" magar unn ka haal yeh hai ke hamaray rasool pay Dur pay un ke paas khuli khuli Hadayat le kar aeye phir bhi un mein bakasrat log zameen mein zyadtyan karne walay hain"
  5,33,"jo log Allah aur is ke rasool se lartay hain aur zameen mein is liye tug o do karte phirtay hain ke fasaad barpaa karen unn ki saza yeh hai ke qatal kiye jayen, ya suli par charhaye jayen, ya unn ke haath aur paon mukhalif simtao se kaat daaley jayen, ya woh jala watan kar diye jayen, yeh zillat o ruswai to unn ke liye duniya mein hai aur akhirat mein unn ke liye is se barri saza hai"
  5,34,magar jo log tauba kar len qabal is ke ke tum un par qaboo pao tumhe maloom hona chahiye ke Allah maaf karne wala aur reham frmane wala hai
  5,35,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, Allah se daro aur uss ki janab mein baar yabi ka zareya talaash karo aur is ki raah mein jad-o-jehad karo, shayad ke tumhe kamyabi naseeb ho jaye"
  5,36,"khoob jaan lau ke jin logon ne kufar ka rawayya ikhtiyar kya hai, agar unn ke qabza mein saari zameen ki doulat ho aur itni hi aur is ke sath, aur woh chahain ke usay Fidya mein day kar roz qayamat ke azaab se bach jayen, tab bhi woh un se qubool nah ki jaye gi aur inhen dard naak saza mil kar rahay gi"
  5,37,woh chahain ge ke dozakh ki aag se nikal bhagain magar nah nikal saken ge aur inhen qaim rehne wala azaab diya jaye ga
  5,38,"aur chor, khuwa aurat ho ya mard, dono ke haath kaat do, yeh unn ki kamaai ka badla hai aur Allah ki taraf se abrtnak saza Allah ki qudrat sab par ghalib hai aur woh Dana o Beena hai"
  5,39,"phir jo zulm karne ke baad tauba kere aur apni islaah kar le to Allah ki nazar inayat phir is par mael ho jaye gi, Allah bohat dar guzar karne wala aur reham frmane wala hai"
  5,40,"kya tum jantay nahi ho ke Allah zameen aur asmano ki saltanat ka maalik hai? jisay chahay saza day aur jisay chahay maaf kar day, woh har cheez ka ikhtiyar rakhta hai"
  5,41,"aePeghamber Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam tumahray liye baais ranj nah hon woh log jo kufar ki raah mein barri taiz-gamidikha rahay hain khuwa woh unn mein se hon jo mun se kehte hain hum imaan laaye magar dil unn ke imaan nahi laaye, ya unn mein se hon jo yahodi ban gay hain, jin ka haal yeh hai ke jhoot ke liye kaan lagatay hain, aur dosray logon ki khatir, jo tumahray paas kabhi nahi aeye, sun gun letay phirtay hain, kitaab Allah ke alfaaz ko unn ka sahih mehal mutayyan honay ke bawajood asal maienay se phertey hain, aur logon se kehte hain ke agar tumhe yeh hukum diya jaye to manu nahi to nah manu jisay Allah hi ne fitnah mein daalnay ka iradah kar liya ho to is ko Allah ki girift se bachanay ke liye tum kuch nahi kar saktay, yeh woh log hain jin ke dilon ko Allah ne pak karna nah chaha, un ke liye duniya mein ruswai hai aur akhirat mein sakht saza"
  5,42,"yeh jhoot suneney walay aur haraam ke maal khanay walay hain, lehaza agar yeh tumahray paas ( apne muqadmaat le kar ) ayen to tumhe ikhtiyar diya jata hai ke chaho un ka faisla karo warna inkaar kar do inkaar kar do to yeh tumhara kuch bigaar nahi satke, aur faisla karo to phir theek theek insaaf ke sath karo ke Allah insaaf karne walon ko pasand karta hai"
  5,43,aur yeh tumhe kaisay hukum banatay hain jabkay un ke paas Touraat mojood hai jis mein Allah ka hukum likha howa hai aur phir yeh is se mun mourr rahay hain? asal baat yeh hai ke yeh log imaan hi nahi rakhtay
  5,44,"hum ne Touraat nazil ki jis mein hadaayat aur roshni thi saaray nabi, jo muslim thay, usi ke mutabiq inn yahodi ban jaane walon ke mamlaat ka faisla karte thay, aur isi terhan Rabbani aur Ahbar bhi ( isi par faisla ka madaar rakhtay thay ) kyunkay inhen kitaab Allah ki hifazat ka zimma daar banaya gaya tha aur woh is par gawah thay pas ( ae giroh yahood! ) tum logon se nah daro balkay mujh se daro aur meri ayaat ko zara zara se muawzay le kar bechna chore do jo log Allah ke nazil kardah qanoon ke mutabiq faisla nah karen wohi kafir hain"
  5,45,"Touraat mein hum ne yahudion par yeh hukum likh diya tha ke jaan ke badlay jaan, aankhh ke badlay aankhh, naak ke badlay naak, kaan ke badlay kaan, daant ke badlay daant, aur tamam zakhamo ke liye barabar ka badla phir jo qisaas ka sadqa kar day to woh is ke liye kaffara hai aur jo log Allah ke nazil kardah qanoon ke mutabiq faisla nah karen wohi zalim hain"
  5,46,phir hum ne un payghambaroon ke baad maryam ke betay eesa ko bheja Touraat mein se jo kuch is ke samnay mojood tha woh is ki tasdeeq karne wala tha aur hum ne is ko injeel ataa ki jis mein rahnumai aur roshni thi aur woh bhi Touraat mein se jo kuch uss waqt mojood tha uss ki tasdeeq karne wali thi aur khuda taras logon ke liye sara sar hadaayat aur nasiyaat thi
  5,47,hamara hukum tha ke ahal injeel is qanoon ke mutabiq faisla karen jo Allah ne is mein nazil kya hai aur jo log Allah ke nazil kardah qanoon ke mutabiq faisla nah karen wohi fasik hain
  5,48,"phir ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! hum ne tumhari taraf yeh kitaab bhaije jo haq le kar aayi hai aur al-kitab mein se jo kuch is ke agay mojood hai uss ki tasdeeq karne wali aur is ki Muhafiz o nigehbaan hai lehaza tum khuda ke nazil kardah qanoon ke mutabiq logon ke mamlaat ka faisla karo aur jo haq tumahray paas aaya hai uss se mun mourr kar un ki khwahisaat ki pairwi nah karo hum ne tum mein se har aik ke liye aik Shariat aur aik raah amal muqarrar ki agarchay tumhara khuda chahta to tum sab ko aik ummat bhi bana sakta tha, lekin uss ne yeh iss liye kya ke jo kuch uss ne tum logon ko diya hai is mein tumhari azmaish kere lehaza bhulaiyon mein aik dosray se Sabqat le jaane ki koshish karo aakhir-kaar tum sab ko khuda ki taraf palat kar jana hai, phir woh tumhe asal haqeeqat bta day ga jis mein tum ikhtilaaf karte rahay ho"
  5,49,"pas ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! tum Allah ke nazil kardah qanoon ke mutabiq inn logon ke mamlaat ka faisla karo aur un ki khwahisaat ki pairwi nah karo hooshiyar raho ke yeh log tum ko fitnah mein daal kar uss hadaayat se zarra barabar munharif nah karne payen jo khuda ne tumhari taraf nazil ki hai phir agar yeh is se mun morhin to jaan lau ke Allah ne inn ke baaz gunaaho ki Padaash mein un ko mbtlaye museebat karne ka iradah hi kar liya hai, aur yeh haqeeqat hai ke inn logon mein se aksar fasik hain"
  5,50,( agar yeh khuda ke qanoon se mun morty hain ) to kya phir jahliat ka faisla chahtay hain? halaank jo log Allah par yaqeen rakhtay hain un ke nazdeek Allah se behtar faisla karne wala koi nahi hai
  5,51,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho! yahudion aur esaion ko apna Rafeeq nah banaao, yeh aapas hi mein aik dosray ke Rafeeq hain aur agar tum mein se koi un ko apna Rafeeq banata hai to is ka shumaar bhi phir unhi mein hai, yaqeenan Allah zaalmon ko apni rahnumai se mahroom kar deta hai"
  5,52,"tum dekhte ho ke jin ke dilon mein nifaq ki bemari hai woh aُnhi mein daud dhoop karte phirtay hain kehte hain"" hamein dar lagta hai ke kahin hum kisi museebat ke chakkar mein nah phas jayen"" magar baeed nahi ke Allah jab tumhe faisla kin fatah bakhshay ga ya apni taraf se koi aur baat zahir kere ga to yeh log apne iss nifaq par jisay yeh dilon mein chupaye hue hain nadim hon ge"
  5,53,"aur uss waqt ahal imaan kahin ge"" kya yeh wohi log hain jo Allah ke naam se kari kari kasmain kha kar yaqeen dilatey thay ke hum tumahray sath hain ?"" un ke sab aamaal zaya hogaye aur aakhir-kaar yeh nakaam o namuraad ho kar rahay"
  5,54,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, agar tum mein se koi apne deen se phirta hai ( to phir jaye ) Allah aur bohat se log aisay peda kar day ga jo Allah ko mehboob hon ge aur Allah unn ko mehboob hoga, jo mominon par naram aur kufar par sakht hon ge, jo Allah ki raah mein jad-o-jehad karen ge aur kisi malamat karne walay ki malamat se nah dareen ge yeh Allah ka fazl hai, jisay chahta hai ataa karta hai Allah wasee zaraye ka maalik hai aur sab kuch jaanta hai"
  5,55,"tumahray Rafeeq to haqeeqat mein sirf Allah aur Allah ka rasool aur woh ahal imaan hain jo namaz qaim karte hain, zkoh dete hain aur Allah ke agay jhuknay walay hain"
  5,56,aur jo Allah aur is ke rasool aur ahal imaan ko apna Rafeeq bana le ussay maloom ho ke Allah ki jamaat hi ghalib rehne wali hai
  5,57,"a y logo jo imaan laaye ho, tumahray paish ro ahal kitaab mein se jin logon ne tumahray deen ko mazaq aur tafreeh ka samaan bana liya hai, unhen aur dosray kafiroon ko apna dost aur Rafeeq nah banaao Allah se daro agar tum momin ho"
  5,58,jab tum namaz ke liye munaadi karte ho to woh is ka mazaq uratay aur is se khailtay hain is ki wajah yeh hai ke woh aqal nahi rakhtay
  5,59,"inn se kaho,"" ae ahal kitaab! tum jis baat par hum se bigre ho woh is ke siwa aur kya hai ke hum Allah par aur deen ki uss taleem par imaan le aeye hain jo hamari taraf nazil hui hai aur hum se pehlay bhi nazil hui thi, aur tum mein se aksar log fasik hain? """
  5,60,"phir kaho"" kya mein unn logon ki nishandahi karoon jin ka anjaam khuda ke haan fasqoon ke anjaam se bhi badter hai? woh jin par khuda ne laanat ki, jin par uss ka ghazab toota, jin mein se bandar aur soor banaye gay, jinhon ne Taghoot ki bandagi ki un ka darja aur bhi ziyada bura hai aur woh sawa al-sabeelse bohat ziyada bhatkay hue hain """
  5,61,"jab yeh tum logon ke paas atay hain to kehte hain ke hum imaan laaye, halaank kufar liye hue aeye thay aur kufar hi liye hue wapas gay aur Allah khoob jaanta hai jo kuch yeh dilon mein chupaye hue hain"
  5,62,tum dekhte ho ke un mein se bakasrat log gunah aur zulm o zayad-ti ke kamon mein daud dhoop karte phirtay hain aur haraam ke maal khatay hain bohat buri harkaat hain jo yeh kar rahay hain
  5,63,kyun inn ke u'lamaa٫ aur mashaiykh inhen gunah par zabaan kholnay aur haraam khanay se nahi roktay? yaqeenan bohat hi bura karnaama zindagi hai jo woh tayyar kar rahay hain
  5,64,"yahodi kehte hain Allah ke haath bandhay hue hain bandhay gay un ke haath, aur laanat pari inn par uss bakwaas ki badolat jo yeh karte hain Allah ke haath to kushadah hain, jis terhan chahta hai kharch karta hai haqeeqat yeh hai ke jo kalaam tumahray rab ki taraf se tum par nazil howa hai woh un mein se aksar logon ki sar kashi o baatil parasti mein ultay izafah ka mojab ban gaya hai, aur ( is ki Padaash mein ) hum ne un ke darmain qayamat taq ke liye adawat aur dushmani daal di hai jab kabhi yeh jung ki aag bhrhkate hain Allah uss ko thanda kar deta hai yeh zameen mein fasaad phelanay ki sae kar rahay hain magar Allah fasaad barpaa karne walon ko hargiz pasand nahi karta"
  5,65,agar ( iss sar kashi ke bajaye ) yeh ahal kitaab imaan le atay aur khuda tarsi ki rawish ikhtiyar karte to hum inn ki buraiyan inn se daur kar dete aur un ko Nemat bharijannaton mein pohanchate
  5,66,kash unhon ne Touraat aur injeel aur unn doosri kitabon ko qaim kya hota jo inn ke rab ki taraf se inn ke paas bhaije gayi theen aisa karte to inn ke liye oopar se rizaq barasta aur neechay se ubalta agarchay inn mein kuch log raast ro bhi hain lekin un ki aksariyat sakht bad amal hai
  5,67,aePeghamber Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam jo kuch tumahray rab ki taraf se tum par nazil kya gaya hai woh logon taq pouncha do agar tum ne aisa nah kya to is ki paigambri ka haq ada nah kya Allah tum ko logon ke shar se bachanay wala hai yaqeen rakho ke woh kafiroon ko ( tumahray muqaabla mein ) kamyabi ki raah hargiz nah dukhaay ga
  5,68,"saaf keh do ke"" ae ahal kitaab! tum hargiz kisi asal par nahi ho jab taq ke Touraat aur injeel aur unn doosri kitabon ko qaim nah karo jo tumahray rab ki taraf se nazil ki gayi hain"" zaroor hai ke yeh farmaan jo tum par nazil kya gaya hai un mein se aksar ki sar kashi aur inkaar ko aur ziyada barha day ga magar inkaar karne walon ke haal par kuch afsos nah karo"
  5,69,"( yaqeen jano ke yahan ajarah kisi ka bhi nahi hai ) musalman ho n ya yahodi, Sabi ho n ya isaai, jo bhi Allah aur roz aakhir par imaan laaye ga aur naik amal kere ga be shak is ke liye nah kisi khauf ka maqam hai nah ranj ka"
  5,70,"hum ne bani Israel se pukhta ehad liya aur unn ki taraf bohat se rasool beje, magar jab kabhi un ke paas koi rasool unn ki khwahisaat nafs ke khilaaf kuch le kar aaya to kisi ko unhon ne jhtlaya aur kisi ko qatal kar diya"
  5,71,"aur apne nazdeek yeh samjhay ke koi fitnah runuma nah hoga, is liye andhay aur behray ban gay phir Allah ne unhen maaf kya to unn mein se aksar log aur ziyada andhay aur behray bantay chalay gay Allah unn ki yeh sab harkaat daikhta raha hai"
  5,72,"yaqeenan kufar kya unn logon ne jinhon ne kaha ke Allah maseeh Ibn maryam hi hai halaank maseeh ne kaha tha ke"" ae bani Israel ! Allah ki bandagi karo jo mera rab bhi hai aur tumhara rab bhi"" jis ne Allah ke sath kisi ko shareek ٹ Tehrayauss par Allah ne jannat haraam kar di aur uss ka thikana jahannum hai aur aisay zaalmon ka koi madad gaar nahi"
  5,73,"yaqeenan kufar kya unn logon ne jinhon ne kaha ke Allah teen mein ka aik hai, halaank aik khuda ke siwa koi khuda nahi hai agar yeh log apni inn baton se baz nah aeye to un mein se jis jis ne kufar kya hai uss ko dard naak saza di jaye gi"
  5,74,phir kya yeh Allah se tauba nah karen ge aur is se maffi nah mangeen ge? Allah bohat dar guzar frmane wala aur reham karne wala hai
  5,75,"maseeh Ibn maryam iss ke siwa kuch nahi ke bas aik rasool tha, uss se pehlay aur bhi bohat se rasool guzar chuke thay, is ki maa aikrasbaaz aurat thi, aur woh dono khana khatay thay, dekho hum kis terhan un ke samnay haqeeqat ki nishanain wazeh karte hain, phir dekho yeh kidhar ultay phir y jatay hain"
  5,76,"inn se kaho, kya tum Allah ko chore kar uss ki parastish karte ho jo nah tumahray liye nuqsaan ka ikhtiyar rakhta hai nah naffa ka? halaank sab ki suneney wala aur sab kuch jan-nay wala to Allah hi hai"
  5,77,"kaho, ae ahal kitaab! apne deen mein na-haq ghallo nah karo aur aُ noon logon ke takhayulaat ki pairwi nah karo jo tum se pehlay khud gumraah hue aur bahuton ko gumraah kya, aur"" sawa as sabeelse bhatak gay"
  5,78,bani Israel mein se jin logon ne kufar ki raah ikhtiyar ki unn par DAWOD aur eesa Ibn maryam ki zabaan se laanat ki gayi kyunkay woh sarkash hogaye thay aur zyadtyan karne lagey thay
  5,79,"onhon ne aik dosray ko buray af-aal ke irtikaab se rokna chore diya tha, bura tarz amal tha jo onhon ne ikhtiyar kya"
  5,80,"aaj tum unn mein bakasrat aisay log dekhte ho jo ( ahal imaan ke muqaabla mein ) kufar ki himayat o rafaqat karte hain yaqeenan bohat bura injaam hai jis ki tayari unn ke nafso-n ne unn ke liye ki hai, Allah unn par ghazab naak ho gaya hai aur woh daimi azaab mein mubtala honay walay hain"
  5,81,agar fi al waqea yeh log Allah aurPeghamber Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallamaur uss cheez ke maan-ne walay hotay jo paighambar par nazil hui thi to kabhi ( ahal imaan ke muqablay mein ) kafiroon ko apna Rafeeq nah banatay magar un mein se to beshtar log khuda ki itaat se nikal chuke hain
  5,82,"tum ahal imaan ki adawat mein sab se ziyada sakht yahood aur mushriqeen ko pao ge, aur imaan laane walon ke liye dosti mein qareeb tar unn logon ko pa o ge jinhon ne kaha tha ke hum nasari hain yeh iss wajah se ke un mein ibadat guzaar aalam aur tarik al-dunia faqeer paye jatay hain aur unn mein ghuroor nafs nahi hai"
  5,83,"jab woh is kalaam ko suntay hain jo rasool par Itra hai to tum dekhte ho ke haq shanasi ke assar se unn ki ankhen aanso-on se tar ho jati hain woh bol uthte hain ke"" parvar-digaar! hum imaan laaye, hamara naam gawahi dainay walon mein likh le """
  5,84,"aur woh kehte hain ke"" aakhir kyun nah hum Allah par imaan layein aur jo haq hamaray paas aaya hai ussay kyun nah maan len jabkay hum iss baat ki khwahish rakhtay hain ke hamara rab hamein Saleh logon mein shaamil kere? """
  5,85,unn ke iss qoul ki wajah se Allah ne unn ko aisi jannaten ataa kee jin ke neechay nhrin behti hain aur woh un mein hamesha rahen ge yeh jaza hai naik rawayya ikhtiyar karne walon ke liye
  5,86,"rahay woh log jinhon ne hamari ayaat ko maan-ne se inkaar kya aur inhen jhtlaya, to woh jahannum ke mustahiq hain"
  5,87,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, jo pak cheeze Allah ne tumahray liye halal ki hain inhen haraam nah kar lau aur hadd se tajawaz nah karo, Allah ko zayad-ti karne walay sakht napasand hain"
  5,88,jo kuch halal o Tayyab rizaq Allah ne tum ko diya hai ussay kha o piyo aur uss khuda ki nafarmani se bachte raho jis par tum imaan laaye ho
  5,89,"tum log jo mehmal kasmain kha letay ho unn par Allah girift nahi karta, magar jo kasmain tum jaan boojh kar khatay ho unn par zaroor tum se muwakhza kere ga ( aisi qisam tornay ka ) kaffara yeh hai ke das miskeeno ko woh ost darjay ka khana khilao jo tum apne baal bachon ko khelati ho, ya inhen kapray peh-nao, ya aik ghulam azad karo, aur jo is ki istetat nah rakhta ho woh teen din ke rozay rakhay yeh tumhari qasmon ka kaffara hai jabkay tum qasam kha kar toar do apni qasmon ki hifazat kya karo is terhan Allah apne ehkaam tumahray liye wazeh karta hai shayad ke tum shukar ada karo"
  5,90,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, yeh sharaab aur juaa aur yeh astane aur panse, yeh sab ganday shaytani kaam hain, un se parhaiz karo, umeed hai ke tumhe Falah naseeb hogi"
  5,91,shetan to yeh chahta hai ke sharaab aur juye ke zareya se tumahray darmain adawat aur bughz daal day aur tumhe khuda ki yaad se aur namaz se rok day phir kya tum un cheezon se baz raho ge ?
  5,92,"Allah aur uss ke rasool ki baat manu aur baz aa jao, lekin agar tum ne hukum aduli ki to jaan lau ke hamaray rasool par bas saaf saaf hukum pouncha dainay ki zimma daari thi"
  5,93,"jo log imaan le aeye aur naik amal karne lagey unhon ne pehlay jo kuch khaya piya tha is par koi girift nah hogi bashart e kay woh aindah unn cheezon se bachay rahen jo haraam ki gayi hain aur imaan par saabit qadam rahen aur achay kaam karen, phir jis jis cheez se roka jaye is se rkin aur jo farmaan Ellahi ho ussay manen, phir khuda tarsi ke sath naik rawayya rakhen Allah naik kirdaar logon ko pasand karta hai"
  5,94,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, Allah tumhe uss shikaar ke zareya se sakht azmaish mein daaley ga jo bilkul tumahray hathon aur nizon ki zad mein hoga, yeh dekhnay ke liye ke tum mein se kon is se ghayebana darta hai, phir jis ne is tanbeeh ke baad Allah ki muqarrar ki hui hadd se tajawaz kya uss ke liye dard naak saza hai"
  5,95,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho! ahraam ki haalat mein shikaar nah maro, aur agar tum mein se koi jaan boojh kar aisa kar guzray to jo janwar is ne mara ho usi ke hum palla aik janwar ussay maweshion mein se Nazar dena hoga jis ka faisla tum mein se do adil aadmi karen ge, aur yeh nazrana kaaba pohanchaya jaye ga, ya nahi to iss gunah ke kaffara mein chand miskeeno ko khana khilana hoga, yaas ke baqadar rozay rakhnay hon ge, taakay woh apne kiye ka maza chakhay pehlay jo ho chuka ussay Allah ne maaf kar diya, lekin ab agar kisi ne is harkat ka iada kya to is se Allah badla le ga, Allah sab par ghalib hai aur badla lainay ki taaqat rakhta hai"
  5,96,"tumahray liye samandar ka shikaar aur is ka khana halal kar diya gaya, jahan tum tehrowahan bhi ussay kha satke ho aur qaafley ke liye zaad raah bhi bana saktay ho Albata khushki ka shikaar jab taq ahraam ki haalat mein ho, tum par haraam kya gaya hai pas bachcho uss khuda ki nafarmani se jis ki paishi mein tum sab ko ghair kar haazir kya jaye ga"
  5,97,"Allah ne makaan mohtaram, kaaba ko logon ke liye ( ijtimai zindagi ke ) qiyam ka zareya banaya aur mah haraam aur qurbani ke janwaron aur qalado-n ko bhi ( iss kaam mein Muawin bana diya ) taakay tumhe maloom ho jaye ke Allah asmano o ray zameen ke sab halaat se bakhabar hai aur ussay har cheez ka ilm hai"
  5,98,khabardaar ho jao! Allah saza dainay mein bhi sakht hai aur is ke sath bohat dar guzar aur reham bhi karne wala hai
  5,99,"rasool par to sirf pegham pouncha dainay ki zimma daari hai, agay tumahray khulay aur chupay sab halaat ka jan-nay wala Allah hai"
  5,100,"aePeghamber Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam inn se keh do ke pak aur napak bahar haal yaksaa nahi hain khuwa napak ki behta t- tumhe kitna hi farifta karne wali ho, pas ae logo jo aqal rakhtay ho! Allah ki nafarmani se bachte raho, umeed hai ke tumhe Falah naseeb hogi"
  5,101,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, aisi baatein nah poocha karo jo tum par zahir kar di jayen to tumhe nagawaar hon, lekin agar tum inhen aisay waqt pucho ge jab ke quran nazil ho raha ho to woh tum par khol di jayen gi ab taq jo kuch tum ne kya ussay Allah ne maaf kar diya, woh dar guzar karne wala aur bard baar hai"
  5,102,"tum se pehlay aik giroh ne isi qisam ke sawalaat kiye thay, phir woh log unhi baton ki wajah se kufar mein mubtala hogaye"
  5,103,Allah ne nah koi bahera muqarrar kya hai nah سائبہ aur nah vaseela aur nah Haam magar yeh kafir Allah par jhooti tohmat lagatay hain aur un mein se aksar be aqal hain ( ke aisay وہمیات ko maan rahay hain )
  5,104,aur jab un se kaha jata hai ke aao uss qanoon ki taraf jo Allah ne nazil kya hai aur aaoPeghamber Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallamki taraf to woh jawab dete hain ke hamaray liye to bas wohi tareeqa kaafi hai jis par hum ne apne baap dada ko paaya hai kya yeh baap dada hi ki taqleed kiye chalay jayen ge khuwa woh kuch nah jantay hon aur sahih rasta ki inhen khabar hi nah ho ?
  5,105,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, apni fikar karo, kisi dosray ki gumraahi se tumhara kuch nahi bigartaa agar tum khud raah raast par ho, Allah ki taraf tum sab ko palat kar jana hai, phir woh tumhe bta day ga ke tum kya karte rahay ho"
  5,106,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, jab tum mein se kisi ki mout ka waqt aa jaye aur woh wasiyat kar raha ho to is ke liye shahadat ka nisaab yeh hai ke tumhari jamaat mein se do sahib Adal aadmi gawah banaye jayen, ya agar tum safar ki haalat mein ho aur wahan mout ki museebat paish aa jaye to ghair mslmon hi mein se do gawah le liye ja-ayn phir agar koi shak par jaye to namaz ke baad dono gawahoon ko ( masjid mein ) rok liya jaye aur woh khuda ki qasam kha kar kahin ke"" hum kisi zaati faiday ke aiwz shahadat baichnay walay nahi hain, aur khuwa koi hamara rishta daar hi kyun nah ho ( hum is ki riayat karne walay nahi ) aur nah khuda wastay ki gawahi ko hum chupaney walay hain, agar hum ne ysa kya to gunah gaaron mein shumaar hon ge """
  5,107,"lekin agar pata chal jaye ke un dono ne apne aap ko gunah mein mubtala kya hai to phir un ki jagah do aur shakhs jo un ki bah nisbat shahadat dainay ke liye ahal tar hon un logon mein se kharray hon jin ki haq talfi hui ho, aur woh khuda ki qasam kha kar kahin ke"" hamari shahadat unn ki shahadat se ziyada Bar haq hai aur hum ne apne gawahi mein koi zayad-ti nahi ki hai, agar hum aisa karen to zaalmon mein se hon ge """
  5,108,"is tareeqa se ziyada tawaqqa ki ja sakti hai ke log theek theek shahadat den ge, ya kam az kam is baat hi ka khauf karen ge ke un ki qasmon ke baad dosri qasmon se kahin un ki tardeed nah ho jaye Allah se daro aur suno, Allah nafarmani karne walon ko apni rahnumai se mahroom kar deta hai"
  5,109,"jis roz Allah sab Rasolo-n ko jama kar ke po chay ga ke tumhe kya jawab diya gaya hai, to woh arz karen ge ke hamein kuch ilm nahi, aap hi tamam posheeda haqeeqaton ko jantay hain"
  5,110,"phir tasawwur karo is mauqa ka jab Allah farmaiye ga ke"" ae maryam ke betay eesa! yaad kar meri is Nemat ko jo mein ne tujhe aur teri maa ko ataa ki thi, mein ne rooh pak se teri madad ki, to gehware mein bhi logon se baat karta tha aur barri Umar ko poanch kar bhi, mein ne tujh ko kitaab aur hikmat aur torat aur injeel ki taleem di, to mere hukum se matti ka patla parinday ki shakal ka banata aur is mein phonkta tha aur woh mere hukum se parindah ban jata tha, to madar zaad andhay aur korhi ko mere hukum se acha karta tha, to mُrdon ko mere hukum se nkalta tha, phir jab to bani Israel ke paas Sarih nishanain le kar pouncha aur jo log un mein se munkir haq thay unhon ne kaha ke yeh nishanain jaadoo giri ke siwa aur kuch nahi hain to mein ne hi tujhe unn se bachaaya"
  5,111,"aur jab mein ne hawarion ko ishara kya ke mujh par aur mere rasool par imaan lao tab onhon ne kaha ke"" hum imaan laaye aur gawah raho ke hum muslim hain """
  5,112,( hawarion ke silsila mein ) yeh waqea bhi yaad rahay ke jab hawarion ne kaha ae eesa Ibn maryam! kya aap ka rab hum par aasman se khanay ka aik khawan utaar sakta hai? to eesa ne kaha Allah se daro agar tum momin ho
  5,113,onhon ne kaha hum bas yeh chahtay hain ke is khawan se khana khayen aur hamaray dil mutmaen hon aur hamein maloom ho jaye ke aap ne jo kuch hum se kaha hai woh sach hai aur hum is par gawah hon
  5,114,"is par eesa Ibn maryam ne dua ki"" khudaaya! hamaray rab! hum par aasman se aik khawan nazil kar jo hamaray liye aur hamaray uglo pichlon ke liye khusi ka mauqa qarar paye aur teri taraf se aik nishani ho, hum ko rizaq day aur to behtareen Razaq hai """
  5,115,"Allah ne jawab diya"" mein uss ko tum par nazil karne wala ho n, magar is ke baad jo tum mein se kufar kere ga usay mein aisi saza dun ga jo duniya mein kisi ko nah di hogi """
  5,116,"gharz jab ( yeh ehsanaat yaad dila kar ) Allah farmaiye ga ke"" ae eesa Ibn maryam! kya to ne logon se kaha tha ke khuda ke siwa mujhe aur meri maa ko bhi khuda bana lau ?"" to woh jawab mein arz kere ga ke"" subhan Allah ! mera yeh kaam nah tha ke woh baat kehta jis ke kehnay ka mujhe haq nah tha, agar mein ne aisi baat kahi hoti, to aap ko zaroor ilm hota, aap jantay hain jo kuch mere dil mein hai aur mein nahi jaanta jo kuch aap ke dil mein hai, aap to saari posheeda haqeeqaton ke aalam hain"
  5,117,"mein ne unn se uss ke siwa kuch nahi kaha jis ka aap ne hukum diya tha, yeh ke Allah ki bandagi karo jo mera rab bhi hai aur tumhara rab bhi mein usi waqt taq un ka nigaran tha jab taq ke mein un ke darmain tha jab aap ne mujhe wapas bulaa liya to aap un par nigaran thay aur aap to saari hi cheezon par nigaran hain"
  5,118,"ab agar aap inhen saza den to woh aap ke bande hain aur agar maaf kar den to aap ghalib aur Dana hain """
  5,119,"tab Allah farmaiye ga"" yeh woh din hai jis mein schon ko unn ki sachaai naffa deti hai, un ke liye aisay baagh hain jin ke neechay nhrin beh rahi hain, yahan woh hamesha rahen ge, Allah un se raazi howa aur woh Allah se, yahi barri kamyabi hai """
  5,120,zameen aur asmano aur tamam mojoodaat ki badshshi Allah hi ke liye hai aur woh har cheez par qudrat rakhta hai
